  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK511">
<l>naṉmaiyun tīmaiyu nāṭi nalampurinta</l>
<l>taṉmaiyā ṉāḷap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He should be employed (by a king), whose nature leads him to choose the good, after having weighed both the evil and the good in any undertaking.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
